<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ṣwt ḥbyby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ṣwth ʿạly ṣwth jmyl ymlạ qlby bkl ḍmạn
 ṣwth ngẖmẗ wyạ nsẖyd ymlạ ạldnyạ bạlạ̉lḥạn
 ṣwt ḥbyby byhms ly wạ̉nạ mạsẖy fy lyl ạlgẖrbẗ
 ṣwt yswʿ ynạdy ʿly yʿdy byn ẓrwfy ạlṣʿbẗ
 ṣwt yʿzy kl ạ̉ḥzạny qlby yqwlly ạlgẖymẗ trwḥ
 ṣwt yrfʿny fy wqt ḍʿfy ṣwt yḥmyny mn kl tjạrb
 ṣwt yḍmny ysyj ḥwly bạʿln ʿly̱ ạ̹blys ạ̉nạ gẖạlb</lyrics>
